<title>UK: Halifax to sell 6.14 mln shares today.</title>
<headline>Halifax to sell 6.14 mln shares today.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-06-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Britain's Halifax Plc said on Tuesday that it has recieved orders to sell around 6.14 million shares, or 0.2 percent, of its issued share capital in a tender today.</p>
<p>It said that bids will be accepted by 1700 GMT from pre-registered institutions and London Stock Exchange member firms.</p>
<p>The mortgage lender has organised a number of tenders for qualifying members since its flotation on June 2.</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 4019</p>
